{author:"Iedilgaurd Yven the Grey",title:"Note",resolved:1b,pages:["Here lies Ixinik's last scrolls, the ones left behind when the Reapers came. They may seem useless, but all are powerful enough in the right hands and in the right situation.

I have locked the door and left the key behind in hopes of keeping the reapers","off the scrolls, when they come... And they will. They will kill us all, or we will give up and kill one another, such is our fate.

Unto you, nameless conqueror, I present these scrolls as the Casters of Ixinik's will that you do what must be done."]}
